P.title: Will Jimmy Neutron be US president in 2025?
P.body: Resolves YES if Jimmy Neutron is president by the end of 2025. Resolves NO otherwise.

Q_and_not_P.title: Will I eat a blueberry tomorrow AND Jimmy Neutron not be US president in 2025?
Q_and_not_P.body: Resolves YES if I eat a blueberry tomorrow AND Jimmy Neutron is not president by the end of 2025. Resolves NO otherwise.

P_or_Q.title: Will either of the following occur: (a) Jimmy Neutron is US president by the end of 2025, or (b) I eat a blueberry tomorrow?
P_or_Q.body: Resolves YES if either of the said events occur (or both). Resolves NO otherwise.
